item.description:
Join the Newcomers to Providence group for what will be a great night of comedy!

From the FishNet-Networks.net web site:

FishNet-NetWorks.net is a hilarious, politically incorrect, parody of a large American computer networking company with an audience-interactive format. “FishNet-Networks.Net” is a fictitious corporation, that sells networking products using the worlds’ fish as the network! Are you confused about the product yet? So are all the employees at FishNet-NetWorks.net!

The fun begins as soon as the audience walks in! Each audience member is now a new employee of FishNet-NetWorks.net! A grand corporate kick-off , or “All Fins” meeting, follows in the company’s “Aquarium” auditorium to welcome all of the new employees, or “guppies” as they are fondly (and annoyingly) called, in a FIN-TASTIC way!

To purchase tickets:

Normally, tickets are $15, but Shiggles Comedy Club is offering a 33% discount to Newcomers members only!

1. Purchase tickets at https://shiggles-come...
2. Select the number of tickets you would like to purchase under "Quantity" and click on "Get Tickets"
3. Enter "meet up" (yes, two words) in the Discount code line and then click on "Apply Discount"
4. You may proceed to check out.

Please note there is a small convenience fee/ticket.

Proceeds will be benefitting the Rhode Island Chapter of the National MS Society.
